Class LevelLoader

  • java.lang.Object
    • game.LevelLoader

  • public class LevelLoader
extends java.lang.Object
    Description:
    Loads graphics corresponding to each stage
    Each level has its own designated map layout of obstacles
    Enemies and characters are also loaded onto map display based on stage level
    Since:
    2014-03-31
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Team 6
